{"type":"message","id":"9597f362","parentId":"dad6c0a4","timestamp":"2026-02-15T18:51:33.699Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 20:51 GMT+2] OPERATION: SACRED SYNCHRONIZATION (META-UPDATE).\n\n1.  **Protocol Audit:**\n    *   Read `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`.\n    *   Read `openclaw.json`.\n    *   Read `docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.json`.\n    *   Read `specs/PRD_TEMPLATE.md`.\n\n2.  **The Meta-Update (`MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`):**\n    *   *Rewrite:* Incorporate \"Swarm Architecture\", \"Terminal OODA\", \"Digital DNA\", \"Reporting Guard\".\n    *   *Constraint:* Do NOT touch bot source code. Only docs.\n\n3.  **System Level Config (`openclaw.json`):**\n    *   *Update:* Add `capabilities: [\"shared_memory\", \"ooda_watchdog\", \"rust_polyglot\"]` (or inject into instructions block if schema restricts).\n\n4.  **Self-Validation (Flash):**\n    *   *Spawn:* `Flash-Validator`.\n    *   *Task:* Read `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`. Extract Top 3 Rules.\n    *   *Criteria:* Must mention OODA, Swarm/Split, and Reporting.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   List of files updated.\n    *   \"The Golden Rule\" quote.\n    *   Flash Verification Report."}],"timestamp":1771181493698}}
