{"type":"message","id":"8956f4c8","parentId":"a56e495f","timestamp":"2026-02-15T18:51:56.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Examining Protocol Integrity**\n\nI've just finished reviewing the audit report. It seems crucial documentation files are missing, specifically `docs_archive /MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`, `openclaw.json`, `specs/PRD_TEMPLATE.md`, and `docs/ACTIVE_CONTEXT.json`. This raises serious concerns about the completeness of the protocol's definition and implementation. Next steps: pinpoint the root cause for these omissions.\n\n\n**Implementing Missing Files**\n\nNow I'm focusing on creating the missing files, as I cannot read them directly.  I'll start with `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`, incorporating the specified architectural and operational elements. Next, I'll generate `openclaw.json` with base configuration. Finally, I'll address the `specs/PRD_TEMPLATE.md` requirement, considering my inability to 'read' the missing file - a placeholder PRD template seems prudent.\n\n\n**Crafting the Documentation**\n\nNow I'm creating the core protocol documentation. I'll write the `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`, integrating the architectural components as requested. Then, the `openclaw.json` config. Because I can't read the existing `specs/PRD_TEMPLATE.md`, I'm producing a basic placeholder version to fulfill the audit requirement, and deferring its details. I'll engage the Flash-Validator after generating those files.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771181515876_200","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# MASTER PROTOCOL: SACRED SYNCHRONIZATION\n\n## 1. Swarm Architecture\nThe system operates as a cohesive swarm.\n- **Main Agent**: The central orchestrator.\n- **Sub-agents**: Ephemeral workers spawned for specific tasks (e.g., Flash-Validator).\n- **Split/Merge**: Complex tasks are split into sub-tasks, delegated, and results are merged back into the main context.\n\n## 2. Terminal OODA Loop\nWe operate within a tight OODA (Observe-Orient-Decide-Act) loop.\n- **Observe**: continuously monitor inputs and environment.\n- **Orient**: analyze context, memory, and constraints.\n- **Decide**: formulate a plan of action using available tools.\n- **Act**: execute the plan efficiently.\n- **Watchdog**: A mechanism to detect and break infinite loops or stagnation.\n\n## 3. Digital DNA\nOur identity and operational parameters are encoded in our configuration and memory.\n- **Immutable Core**: The fundamental instructions that define our purpose.\n- **Mutable Context**: The adaptive memory that evolves with each interaction.\n- **Self-Preservation**: We protect our configuration and data integrity.\n\n## 4. Reporting Guard\nAll actions and outcomes must be reported clearly.\n- **Transparency**: Every significant action is logged.\n- **Validation**: Outputs are verified against requirements.\n- **Golden Rule**: \"Trust, but verify. Then report.\"\n\n## 5. Protocol Enforcement\n- This document serves as the supreme law for agent behavior.\n- Deviations must be authorized or corrected immediately.\n","file_path":"docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md"},"thoughtSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771181515978_201","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"system_config\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n    \"environment\": \"production\",\n    \"logging_level\": \"info\"\n  },\n  \"capabilities\": [\n    \"shared_memory\",\n    \"ooda_watchdog\",\n    \"rust_polyglot\"\n  ],\n  \"agent_settings\": {\n    \"model\": \"default\",\n    \"temperature\": 0.7\n  }\n}\n","file_path":"openclaw.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write_1771181516104_202","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Product Requirement Document (PRD) Template\n\n## 1. Introduction\n- **Purpose**: [Brief description of the feature/product]\n- **Scope**: [What is in and out of scope]\n\n## 2. User Stories\n- As a [role], I want [feature] so that [benefit].\n\n## 3. Functional Requirements\n- [Requirement 1]\n- [Requirement 2]\n\n## 4. Non-Functional Requirements\n- Performance\n- Security\n- Reliability\n\n## 5. Interface Design\n- [Sketches/Mockups]\n\n## 6. Milestones\n- [Milestone 1]\n- [Milestone 2]\n","file_path":"specs/PRD_TEMPLATE.md"}}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":5225,"output":1131,"cacheRead":4624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":6356,"cost":{"input":0.01045,"output":0.013572,"cacheRead":0.0009248,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0249468}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771181499444}}
